description:
The Jester is a Ultimate Surrender fan favorite. Her smack talk, jovial attitude on the mat, and wrestling skill has earned her a huge following. When she dropped out of the top 10 rankings, there was a roar of protest.
The Gymnast is a rock hard, buff specimen of female perfection and beauty. Her wrestling experience is starting to sink in and she is becoming a star at US. Even giving up 25lbs she dominates the Jester by forcing 2 submissions. Rd4 had some of our best foot worship and hard fucking we’ve seen yet.
title: The Gymnast (2-5) Ranked 10th
